{"tid":1833482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺應該趕絕班支那人唔俾佢哋嚟買口罩？","createTime":"2020-01-22T02:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T03:43:11.000Z","uid":53610,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ceed4e39f5961cbca96fdd65016606db38544a56","tid":1833482,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:15:10.000Z","msg":"大陸依家基本上口罩嚴重短缺，一係炒到勁貴，可以預料不久的將來將會有大批水貨客擁入搶購口罩<br />\n俾佢哋咁搶一搶實搶晒香港啲口罩，到時就到我哋冇口罩用，死撚晒<br />\n喺依個生死存亡之際，係咪應該高舉本地優先的旗幟，搞返個保衛口罩光復上水大行動，參考限奶令倡議限口罩令，捍衛我哋用口罩保護自己生命安全的權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">最重要趕絕晒班仆街，我要佢哋冇口罩用死清光</span>"},{"pid":"c1a1a26ee66bdd64535a76becc1d5759e57f4c50","tid":1833482,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:30:04.000Z","msg":"同樣，為咗廣大市民安全應該封撚埋個西九高鐵站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aca3c729455de084dbec2583f2ae5637bbf03fe","tid":1833482,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:42:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3474364197ed214bc1153b9167d065b281aadc4","tid":1833482,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:51:54.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8f7ae5e26deb99b678fa7be8dde550dc7b9cb6","tid":1833482,"uid":27319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T03:06:19.000Z","msg":"口罩照喺amazon 買 跟著喺上水高價賣返畀佢地 用敵家嘅錢資助香港抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64e82cbf8c5ce44f63cb89779ca5fa571637962","tid":1833482,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df8f7ae5e26deb99b678fa7be8dde550dc7b9cb6","tid":1833482,"uid":27319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T03:06:19.000Z","msg":"口罩照喺amazon 買 跟著喺上水高價賣返畀佢地 用敵家嘅錢資助香港抗爭<img src=\"/assets/fac